    "result": {"data":{"allMarkdownRemark":{"edges":[{"node":{"html":"<h1>useState 만들어보기</h1>\n<p>setState를 이용해 값을 바꾸면 새롭게 렌더링 되는데 어떻게 초기값이 아닌 바뀐 값으로 유지될 수 있을까?</p>\n<p>useState를 Javascript로 만들어보며 알아보았다.</p>\n<p>버튼을 누르면 lists에 1씩 증가된 값이 추가되는 형태를 만들어보자.</p>\n<h4>HTML</h4>\n<h4><span class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\" style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 768px; \">\n      <a class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\" href=\"/static/0a5dce8cf3ecbd5c266f02fb41f6bf24/bb42b/%EB%AC%B4%EC%A0%9C.png\" style=\"display: block\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">\n    <span class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\" style=\"padding-bottom: 10.416666666666668%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,iVBORw0KGgoAAAANSUhEUgAAABQAAAACCAYAAABYBvyLAAAACXBIWXMAAAsTAAALEwEAmpwYAAAAN0lEQVQI12Mw1VX7r6Gt9l9JSQmMFRQU/isqKpKMYfoYVFRU/xto6vxX09T4r6aqRpaBMD0gGgCIqjfR0mxaJQAAAABJRU5ErkJggg=='); background-size: cover; display: block;\"></span>\n  <picture>\n          <source srcset=\"/static/0a5dce8cf3ecbd5c266f02fb41f6bf24/a59e9/%EB%AC%B4%EC%A0%9C.webp 192w,\n/static/0a5dce8cf3ecbd5c266f02fb41f6bf24/0ca9f/%EB%AC%B4%EC%A0%9C.webp 384w,\n/static/0a5dce8cf3ecbd5c266f02fb41f6bf24/dc9b9/%EB%AC%B4%EC%A0%9C.webp 768w,\n/static/0a5dce8cf3ecbd5c266f02fb41f6bf24/e2c2f/%EB%AC%B4%EC%A0%9C.webp 1152w,\n/static/0a5dce8cf3ecbd5c266f02fb41f6bf24/f3efb/%EB%AC%B4%EC%A0%9C.webp 1536w,\n/static/0a5dce8cf3ecbd5c266f02fb41f6bf24/9be6c/%EB%AC%B4%EC%A0%9C.webp 2682w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) 100vw, 768px\" type=\"image/webp\">\n          <source srcset=\"/static/0a5dce8cf3ecbd5c266f02fb41f6bf24/3b721/%EB%AC%B4%EC%A0%9C.png 192w,\n/static/0a5dce8cf3ecbd5c266f02fb41f6bf24/66595/%EB%AC%B4%EC%A0%9C.png 384w,\n/static/0a5dce8cf3ecbd5c266f02fb41f6bf24/fe486/%EB%AC%B4%EC%A0%9C.png 768w,\n/static/0a5dce8cf3ecbd5c266f02fb41f6bf24/d2d74/%EB%AC%B4%EC%A0%9C.png 1152w,\n/static/0a5dce8cf3ecbd5c266f02fb41f6bf24/e8464/%EB%AC%B4%EC%A0%9C.png 1536w,\n/static/0a5dce8cf3ecbd5c266f02fb41f6bf24/bb42b/%EB%AC%B4%EC%A0%9C.png 2682w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) 100vw, 768px\" type=\"image/png\">\n          <img class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\" src=\"/static/0a5dce8cf3ecbd5c266f02fb41f6bf24/fe486/%EB%AC%B4%EC%A0%9C.png\" alt=\"  \" title=\"  \" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\">\n        </picture>\n  </a>\n    </span></h4>\n<h4>JS</h4>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 768px; \"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/691ec7beaf3cbb607b6817158b5e7c4c/e52c7/%EB%AC%B4%EC%A0%9C2.png\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 33.33333333333333%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <picture>\n          <source\n              srcset=\"/static/691ec7beaf3cbb607b6817158b5e7c4c/a59e9/%EB%AC%B4%EC%A0%9C2.webp 192w,\n/static/691ec7beaf3cbb607b6817158b5e7c4c/0ca9f/%EB%AC%B4%EC%A0%9C2.webp 384w,\n/static/691ec7beaf3cbb607b6817158b5e7c4c/dc9b9/%EB%AC%B4%EC%A0%9C2.webp 768w,\n/static/691ec7beaf3cbb607b6817158b5e7c4c/e2c2f/%EB%AC%B4%EC%A0%9C2.webp 1152w,\n/static/691ec7beaf3cbb607b6817158b5e7c4c/f3efb/%EB%AC%B4%EC%A0%9C2.webp 1536w,\n/static/691ec7beaf3cbb607b6817158b5e7c4c/2ae4e/%EB%AC%B4%EC%A0%9C2.webp 2146w\"\n              sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) 100vw, 768px\"\n              type=\"image/webp\"\n            />\n          <source\n            srcset=\"/static/691ec7beaf3cbb607b6817158b5e7c4c/3b721/%EB%AC%B4%EC%A0%9C2.png 192w,\n/static/691ec7beaf3cbb607b6817158b5e7c4c/66595/%EB%AC%B4%EC%A0%9C2.png 384w,\n/static/691ec7beaf3cbb607b6817158b5e7c4c/fe486/%EB%AC%B4%EC%A0%9C2.png 768w,\n/static/691ec7beaf3cbb607b6817158b5e7c4c/d2d74/%EB%AC%B4%EC%A0%9C2.png 1152w,\n/static/691ec7beaf3cbb607b6817158b5e7c4c/e8464/%EB%AC%B4%EC%A0%9C2.png 1536w,\n/static/691ec7beaf3cbb607b6817158b5e7c4c/e52c7/%EB%AC%B4%EC%A0%9C2.png 2146w\"\n            sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) 100vw, 768px\"\n            type=\"image/png\"\n          />\n          <img\n            class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n            src=\"/static/691ec7beaf3cbb607b6817158b5e7c4c/fe486/%EB%AC%B4%EC%A0%9C2.png\"\n            alt=\"무제2\"\n            title=\"무제2\"\n            loading=\"lazy\"\n            decoding=\"async\"\n            style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n          />\n        </picture>\n  </a>\n    </span></p>\n<p>List 컴포넌트는 위와 같이 만들었다.</p>\n<ol>\n<li>useState로부터 numArr와 setNumArr를 받는다.</li>\n<li>버튼을 클릭하면 setNumArr에 콜백 함수를 넘겨준다.</li>\n<li>numArr로부터 li 태그를 만들고</li>\n<li>string을 리턴한다.</li>\n</ol>\n<p>이제 useState를 만들어보면</p>\n<span class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\" style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 768px; \">\n      <a class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\" href=\"/static/48f281a0261191a3b8e6fb28c71b5cac/79586/%EB%AC%B4%EC%A0%9C3.png\" style=\"display: block\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">\n    <span class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\" style=\"padding-bottom: 91.66666666666667%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"></span>\n  <picture>\n          <source srcset=\"/static/48f281a0261191a3b8e6fb28c71b5cac/a59e9/%EB%AC%B4%EC%A0%9C3.webp 192w,\n/static/48f281a0261191a3b8e6fb28c71b5cac/0ca9f/%EB%AC%B4%EC%A0%9C3.webp 384w,\n/static/48f281a0261191a3b8e6fb28c71b5cac/dc9b9/%EB%AC%B4%EC%A0%9C3.webp 768w,\n/static/48f281a0261191a3b8e6fb28c71b5cac/21cee/%EB%AC%B4%EC%A0%9C3.webp 932w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) 100vw, 768px\" type=\"image/webp\">\n          <source srcset=\"/static/48f281a0261191a3b8e6fb28c71b5cac/3b721/%EB%AC%B4%EC%A0%9C3.png 192w,\n/static/48f281a0261191a3b8e6fb28c71b5cac/66595/%EB%AC%B4%EC%A0%9C3.png 384w,\n/static/48f281a0261191a3b8e6fb28c71b5cac/fe486/%EB%AC%B4%EC%A0%9C3.png 768w,\n/static/48f281a0261191a3b8e6fb28c71b5cac/79586/%EB%AC%B4%EC%A0%9C3.png 932w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) 100vw, 768px\" type=\"image/png\">\n          <img class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\" src=\"/static/48f281a0261191a3b8e6fb28c71b5cac/fe486/%EB%AC%B4%EC%A0%9C3.png\" alt=\"무제3\" title=\"무제3\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\">\n        </picture>\n  </a>\n    </span>\n<ol>\n<li>useState는 초기값을 받는다.</li>\n<li>그리고 상태를 저장하기 위해 외부에 저장된 state를 이용하고, state가 없으면 초기값으로 설정한다.</li>\n<li>state와 setNumArr를 위한 콜백 함수를 return 해주는데, 만약 인자로 들어오는 값이 함수라면 prev를 위해 state를 인자로 넣어 실행시키고, state를 업데이트해준다.</li>\n<li>block이 함수가 아니라면 바로 state에 할당한다.</li>\n<li>업데이트된 값을 컴포넌트에 적용하기 위해 재렌더링을 시켜준다.</li>\n</ol>\n<p>이제 render를 만들어보자.</p>\n<p>render가 발생하면 app을 초기화 시키고, 가장 최신의 List 리턴값을 반영해야 하므로 다음과 같이 작성했다.</p>\n<span class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\" style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 768px; \">\n      <a class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\" href=\"/static/1ef10c53ebfb6a2f4a3e7da73621c665/bb42b/%EB%AC%B4%EC%A0%9C4.png\" style=\"display: block\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">\n    <span class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\" style=\"padding-bottom: 11.979166666666668%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,iVBORw0KGgoAAAANSUhEUgAAABQAAAACCAYAAABYBvyLAAAACXBIWXMAAAsTAAALEwEAmpwYAAAAS0lEQVQI15WMSQqAMBDA+pRWZ6bazZb+/20RBcGT4CHkEuLqZpQ2SOUg5YLojmjETAgh4L2//cXTXHbLqow+GXOSa8diQtR+Dd/dCeASOKmMDCepAAAAAElFTkSuQmCC'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"></span>\n  <picture>\n          <source srcset=\"/static/1ef10c53ebfb6a2f4a3e7da73621c665/a59e9/%EB%AC%B4%EC%A0%9C4.webp 192w,\n/static/1ef10c53ebfb6a2f4a3e7da73621c665/0ca9f/%EB%AC%B4%EC%A0%9C4.webp 384w,\n/static/1ef10c53ebfb6a2f4a3e7da73621c665/dc9b9/%EB%AC%B4%EC%A0%9C4.webp 768w,\n/static/1ef10c53ebfb6a2f4a3e7da73621c665/e2c2f/%EB%AC%B4%EC%A0%9C4.webp 1152w,\n/static/1ef10c53ebfb6a2f4a3e7da73621c665/f3efb/%EB%AC%B4%EC%A0%9C4.webp 1536w,\n/static/1ef10c53ebfb6a2f4a3e7da73621c665/9be6c/%EB%AC%B4%EC%A0%9C4.webp 2682w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) 100vw, 768px\" type=\"image/webp\">\n          <source srcset=\"/static/1ef10c53ebfb6a2f4a3e7da73621c665/3b721/%EB%AC%B4%EC%A0%9C4.png 192w,\n/static/1ef10c53ebfb6a2f4a3e7da73621c665/66595/%EB%AC%B4%EC%A0%9C4.png 384w,\n/static/1ef10c53ebfb6a2f4a3e7da73621c665/fe486/%EB%AC%B4%EC%A0%9C4.png 768w,\n/static/1ef10c53ebfb6a2f4a3e7da73621c665/d2d74/%EB%AC%B4%EC%A0%9C4.png 1152w,\n/static/1ef10c53ebfb6a2f4a3e7da73621c665/e8464/%EB%AC%B4%EC%A0%9C4.png 1536w,\n/static/1ef10c53ebfb6a2f4a3e7da73621c665/bb42b/%EB%AC%B4%EC%A0%9C4.png 2682w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) 100vw, 768px\" type=\"image/png\">\n          <img class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\" src=\"/static/1ef10c53ebfb6a2f4a3e7da73621c665/fe486/%EB%AC%B4%EC%A0%9C4.png\" alt=\"무제4\" title=\"무제4\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\">\n        </picture>\n  </a>\n    </span>\n<ol>\n<li>\n<p>렌더가 발생된다면 초기값이 아닌 최신 값의 state를 반영하기 위해 외부에 state를 선언했다.</p>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p>render가 호출되면 app을 가져온 뒤, List 함수를 넣어준다.</p>\n</li>\n</ol>\n<div align=\"center\">\n   <img src=\"/df608127ca78e5b023920b6ca2b62ed0/useState.gif\" alt=\"ezgif.com-gif-maker (16)\" width=\"50%\">\n<div></div></div>\n<p>다른 상태까지 추가된다면 어떨까?</p>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 768px; \"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/1becf208b1b273882d9ede0e139a1ead/80b75/%EB%AC%B4%EC%A0%9C5.png\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 51.5625%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <picture>\n          <source\n              srcset=\"/static/1becf208b1b273882d9ede0e139a1ead/a59e9/%EB%AC%B4%EC%A0%9C5.webp 192w,\n/static/1becf208b1b273882d9ede0e139a1ead/0ca9f/%EB%AC%B4%EC%A0%9C5.webp 384w,\n/static/1becf208b1b273882d9ede0e139a1ead/dc9b9/%EB%AC%B4%EC%A0%9C5.webp 768w,\n/static/1becf208b1b273882d9ede0e139a1ead/e2c2f/%EB%AC%B4%EC%A0%9C5.webp 1152w,\n/static/1becf208b1b273882d9ede0e139a1ead/f3efb/%EB%AC%B4%EC%A0%9C5.webp 1536w,\n/static/1becf208b1b273882d9ede0e139a1ead/b9187/%EB%AC%B4%EC%A0%9C5.webp 2118w\"\n              sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) 100vw, 768px\"\n              type=\"image/webp\"\n            />\n          <source\n            srcset=\"/static/1becf208b1b273882d9ede0e139a1ead/3b721/%EB%AC%B4%EC%A0%9C5.png 192w,\n/static/1becf208b1b273882d9ede0e139a1ead/66595/%EB%AC%B4%EC%A0%9C5.png 384w,\n/static/1becf208b1b273882d9ede0e139a1ead/fe486/%EB%AC%B4%EC%A0%9C5.png 768w,\n/static/1becf208b1b273882d9ede0e139a1ead/d2d74/%EB%AC%B4%EC%A0%9C5.png 1152w,\n/static/1becf208b1b273882d9ede0e139a1ead/e8464/%EB%AC%B4%EC%A0%9C5.png 1536w,\n/static/1becf208b1b273882d9ede0e139a1ead/80b75/%EB%AC%B4%EC%A0%9C5.png 2118w\"\n            sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) 100vw, 768px\"\n            type=\"image/png\"\n          />\n          <img\n            class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n            src=\"/static/1becf208b1b273882d9ede0e139a1ead/fe486/%EB%AC%B4%EC%A0%9C5.png\"\n            alt=\"무제5\"\n            title=\"무제5\"\n            loading=\"lazy\"\n            decoding=\"async\"\n            style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n          />\n        </picture>\n  </a>\n    </span></p>\n<ol>\n<li>isClicked라는 상태를 추가했다.</li>\n<li>클릭! 버튼을 누르면 isClicked의 상태가 true, false로 번갈아 바뀌어야 한다.</li>\n</ol>\n<p>확인해 보면 그렇지 않다는 것을 알 수 있다.</p>\n<div align=\"center\">\n   <img src=\"/e14c84b72aaa46cf465f8f1b7b07e648/useState2.gif\" alt=\"ezgif.com-gif-maker (13)\" width=\"50%\">\n<div></div></div>\n<p>바로 외부에 저장한 state로 numArr, isClicked 모두를 관리하려고 해서 그렇기 때문이다.</p>\n<p>따라서 여러 개의 컴포넌트 혹은 여러 개의 상태에 대응하기 위해서는 외부에 state를 저장할 저장 공간이 필요하다는 것을 알 수 있다.</p>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 768px; \"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/82a37d8655667008f726b2e9049eca29/a1898/%EB%AC%B4%EC%A0%9C6.png\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 62.5%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <picture>\n          <source\n              srcset=\"/static/82a37d8655667008f726b2e9049eca29/a59e9/%EB%AC%B4%EC%A0%9C6.webp 192w,\n/static/82a37d8655667008f726b2e9049eca29/0ca9f/%EB%AC%B4%EC%A0%9C6.webp 384w,\n/static/82a37d8655667008f726b2e9049eca29/dc9b9/%EB%AC%B4%EC%A0%9C6.webp 768w,\n/static/82a37d8655667008f726b2e9049eca29/e2c2f/%EB%AC%B4%EC%A0%9C6.webp 1152w,\n/static/82a37d8655667008f726b2e9049eca29/f3efb/%EB%AC%B4%EC%A0%9C6.webp 1536w,\n/static/82a37d8655667008f726b2e9049eca29/0f8fb/%EB%AC%B4%EC%A0%9C6.webp 1674w\"\n              sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) 100vw, 768px\"\n              type=\"image/webp\"\n            />\n          <source\n            srcset=\"/static/82a37d8655667008f726b2e9049eca29/3b721/%EB%AC%B4%EC%A0%9C6.png 192w,\n/static/82a37d8655667008f726b2e9049eca29/66595/%EB%AC%B4%EC%A0%9C6.png 384w,\n/static/82a37d8655667008f726b2e9049eca29/fe486/%EB%AC%B4%EC%A0%9C6.png 768w,\n/static/82a37d8655667008f726b2e9049eca29/d2d74/%EB%AC%B4%EC%A0%9C6.png 1152w,\n/static/82a37d8655667008f726b2e9049eca29/e8464/%EB%AC%B4%EC%A0%9C6.png 1536w,\n/static/82a37d8655667008f726b2e9049eca29/a1898/%EB%AC%B4%EC%A0%9C6.png 1674w\"\n            sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) 100vw, 768px\"\n            type=\"image/png\"\n          />\n          <img\n            class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n            src=\"/static/82a37d8655667008f726b2e9049eca29/fe486/%EB%AC%B4%EC%A0%9C6.png\"\n            alt=\"무제6\"\n            title=\"무제6\"\n            loading=\"lazy\"\n            decoding=\"async\"\n            style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n          />\n        </picture>\n  </a>\n    </span></p>\n<p>stateStore라는 객체 저장 공간을 생성한 뒤, key 값으로는 init을 주었다. 이렇게 하면 useState를 사용할 때마다 key 값으로 저장 공간에 값이 저장되기 때문에 독립적으로 이용할 수 있게 된다.</p>\n<div align=\"center\">\n   <img src=\"/e5c8c36cdff5cb3e552d5f1c16d5e224/useState3.gif\" alt=\"ezgif.com-gif-maker (14)\" width=\"50%\">\n<div></div></div>\n<p>하지만 한 가지 문제가 있다. 바로 key 값이 고유하지 않다는 것인데, 현재는 key를 useState의 초기값인 init으로 주었기 때문에 다른 곳에서 같은 init으로 useState를 생성하게 되면 겹치는 문제가 생긴다.</p>\n<p>이를 해결하기 위해 초기값이 아닌 고유한 값으로 key를 설정할 필요가 있다.</p>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 768px; \"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/e41ad35813bbd1294ac7041aa64d6c19/0d1d8/%EB%AC%B4%EC%A0%9C7.png\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 50%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <picture>\n          <source\n              srcset=\"/static/e41ad35813bbd1294ac7041aa64d6c19/a59e9/%EB%AC%B4%EC%A0%9C7.webp 192w,\n/static/e41ad35813bbd1294ac7041aa64d6c19/0ca9f/%EB%AC%B4%EC%A0%9C7.webp 384w,\n/static/e41ad35813bbd1294ac7041aa64d6c19/dc9b9/%EB%AC%B4%EC%A0%9C7.webp 768w,\n/static/e41ad35813bbd1294ac7041aa64d6c19/e2c2f/%EB%AC%B4%EC%A0%9C7.webp 1152w,\n/static/e41ad35813bbd1294ac7041aa64d6c19/f3efb/%EB%AC%B4%EC%A0%9C7.webp 1536w,\n/static/e41ad35813bbd1294ac7041aa64d6c19/7dcdc/%EB%AC%B4%EC%A0%9C7.webp 2758w\"\n              sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) 100vw, 768px\"\n              type=\"image/webp\"\n            />\n          <source\n            srcset=\"/static/e41ad35813bbd1294ac7041aa64d6c19/3b721/%EB%AC%B4%EC%A0%9C7.png 192w,\n/static/e41ad35813bbd1294ac7041aa64d6c19/66595/%EB%AC%B4%EC%A0%9C7.png 384w,\n/static/e41ad35813bbd1294ac7041aa64d6c19/fe486/%EB%AC%B4%EC%A0%9C7.png 768w,\n/static/e41ad35813bbd1294ac7041aa64d6c19/d2d74/%EB%AC%B4%EC%A0%9C7.png 1152w,\n/static/e41ad35813bbd1294ac7041aa64d6c19/e8464/%EB%AC%B4%EC%A0%9C7.png 1536w,\n/static/e41ad35813bbd1294ac7041aa64d6c19/0d1d8/%EB%AC%B4%EC%A0%9C7.png 2758w\"\n            sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) 100vw, 768px\"\n            type=\"image/png\"\n          />\n          <img\n            class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n            src=\"/static/e41ad35813bbd1294ac7041aa64d6c19/fe486/%EB%AC%B4%EC%A0%9C7.png\"\n            alt=\"무제7\"\n            title=\"무제7\"\n            loading=\"lazy\"\n            decoding=\"async\"\n            style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n          />\n        </picture>\n  </a>\n    </span></p>\n<p>이를 위해 외부에서 key를 관리하기로 했다. 흐름을 살펴보면</p>\n<p>useState가 실행될 때마다 stateStore의 key에 정보가 저장되고, key를 1씩 증가한다. 이렇게 하면 현재</p>\n<ol>\n<li>\n<p>stateStore[0] = block(stateStore[0])으로,</p>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p>stateStore[1] = block으로 저장이 된다.</p>\n</li>\n</ol>\n<p>그리고 setState가 실행되면 재렌더링이 발생하는데, 이때 key 값을 0으로 초기화해야 stateStore에 저장해놓았던 데이터에 접근할 수 있다. 만약 초기화하지 않으면 key 값은 계속 증가하기 때문에 기존 정보에 접근할 수 없게 된다.</p>\n<p>그리고 가장 중요한 부분이</p>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 768px; \"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/de1e9fcd75b6e666d75be34ae9ec9a07/0d1d8/%EB%AC%B4%EC%A0%9C8.png\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 8.333333333333332%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,iVBORw0KGgoAAAANSUhEUgAAABQAAAACCAYAAABYBvyLAAAACXBIWXMAAAsTAAALEwEAmpwYAAAAMUlEQVQI12NQVlb7r6Kq+l9FReW/oqLSfwUFhf+KiopkYwZDE8v/BsYm/3X19KliIACKLTgA+hHFZgAAAABJRU5ErkJggg=='); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <picture>\n          <source\n              srcset=\"/static/de1e9fcd75b6e666d75be34ae9ec9a07/a59e9/%EB%AC%B4%EC%A0%9C8.webp 192w,\n/static/de1e9fcd75b6e666d75be34ae9ec9a07/0ca9f/%EB%AC%B4%EC%A0%9C8.webp 384w,\n/static/de1e9fcd75b6e666d75be34ae9ec9a07/dc9b9/%EB%AC%B4%EC%A0%9C8.webp 768w,\n/static/de1e9fcd75b6e666d75be34ae9ec9a07/e2c2f/%EB%AC%B4%EC%A0%9C8.webp 1152w,\n/static/de1e9fcd75b6e666d75be34ae9ec9a07/f3efb/%EB%AC%B4%EC%A0%9C8.webp 1536w,\n/static/de1e9fcd75b6e666d75be34ae9ec9a07/7dcdc/%EB%AC%B4%EC%A0%9C8.webp 2758w\"\n              sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) 100vw, 768px\"\n              type=\"image/webp\"\n            />\n          <source\n            srcset=\"/static/de1e9fcd75b6e666d75be34ae9ec9a07/3b721/%EB%AC%B4%EC%A0%9C8.png 192w,\n/static/de1e9fcd75b6e666d75be34ae9ec9a07/66595/%EB%AC%B4%EC%A0%9C8.png 384w,\n/static/de1e9fcd75b6e666d75be34ae9ec9a07/fe486/%EB%AC%B4%EC%A0%9C8.png 768w,\n/static/de1e9fcd75b6e666d75be34ae9ec9a07/d2d74/%EB%AC%B4%EC%A0%9C8.png 1152w,\n/static/de1e9fcd75b6e666d75be34ae9ec9a07/e8464/%EB%AC%B4%EC%A0%9C8.png 1536w,\n/static/de1e9fcd75b6e666d75be34ae9ec9a07/0d1d8/%EB%AC%B4%EC%A0%9C8.png 2758w\"\n            sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) 100vw, 768px\"\n            type=\"image/png\"\n          />\n          <img\n            class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n            src=\"/static/de1e9fcd75b6e666d75be34ae9ec9a07/fe486/%EB%AC%B4%EC%A0%9C8.png\"\n            alt=\"무제8\"\n            title=\"무제8\"\n            loading=\"lazy\"\n            decoding=\"async\"\n            style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n          />\n        </picture>\n  </a>\n    </span></p>\n<p>위 부분인데, key 값을 현재 스코프에 고정시키는 역할을 한다. 만약 storeKey로 key를 고정시키지 않는다면 render할 때마다 key를 0으로 초기화 하기 때문에 클릭이 일어나면 항상 stateStore[0]에 접근하게 된다. 예를 들어</p>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 768px; \"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/5f591d91eb8c216d35b5a9b7b0cd62cf/9ddde/%EB%AC%B4%EC%A0%9C9.png\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 49.479166666666664%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <picture>\n          <source\n              srcset=\"/static/5f591d91eb8c216d35b5a9b7b0cd62cf/a59e9/%EB%AC%B4%EC%A0%9C9.webp 192w,\n/static/5f591d91eb8c216d35b5a9b7b0cd62cf/0ca9f/%EB%AC%B4%EC%A0%9C9.webp 384w,\n/static/5f591d91eb8c216d35b5a9b7b0cd62cf/dc9b9/%EB%AC%B4%EC%A0%9C9.webp 768w,\n/static/5f591d91eb8c216d35b5a9b7b0cd62cf/e2c2f/%EB%AC%B4%EC%A0%9C9.webp 1152w,\n/static/5f591d91eb8c216d35b5a9b7b0cd62cf/f3efb/%EB%AC%B4%EC%A0%9C9.webp 1536w,\n/static/5f591d91eb8c216d35b5a9b7b0cd62cf/e1a50/%EB%AC%B4%EC%A0%9C9.webp 2784w\"\n              sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) 100vw, 768px\"\n              type=\"image/webp\"\n            />\n          <source\n            srcset=\"/static/5f591d91eb8c216d35b5a9b7b0cd62cf/3b721/%EB%AC%B4%EC%A0%9C9.png 192w,\n/static/5f591d91eb8c216d35b5a9b7b0cd62cf/66595/%EB%AC%B4%EC%A0%9C9.png 384w,\n/static/5f591d91eb8c216d35b5a9b7b0cd62cf/fe486/%EB%AC%B4%EC%A0%9C9.png 768w,\n/static/5f591d91eb8c216d35b5a9b7b0cd62cf/d2d74/%EB%AC%B4%EC%A0%9C9.png 1152w,\n/static/5f591d91eb8c216d35b5a9b7b0cd62cf/e8464/%EB%AC%B4%EC%A0%9C9.png 1536w,\n/static/5f591d91eb8c216d35b5a9b7b0cd62cf/9ddde/%EB%AC%B4%EC%A0%9C9.png 2784w\"\n            sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) 100vw, 768px\"\n            type=\"image/png\"\n          />\n          <img\n            class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n            src=\"/static/5f591d91eb8c216d35b5a9b7b0cd62cf/fe486/%EB%AC%B4%EC%A0%9C9.png\"\n            alt=\"무제9\"\n            title=\"무제9\"\n            loading=\"lazy\"\n            decoding=\"async\"\n            style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n          />\n        </picture>\n  </a>\n    </span></p>\n<p>이렇게 하면 key는 항상 0이 되기 때문에 setState 부분 에서 Key를 참조할 때 항상 0을 가져오게 된다. 따라서 위와 같이 작성하면 정상적으로 값을 출력할 수 없다.</p>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 768px; \"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/de1e9fcd75b6e666d75be34ae9ec9a07/0d1d8/%EB%AC%B4%EC%A0%9C8.png\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 8.333333333333332%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,iVBORw0KGgoAAAANSUhEUgAAABQAAAACCAYAAABYBvyLAAAACXBIWXMAAAsTAAALEwEAmpwYAAAAMUlEQVQI12NQVlb7r6Kq+l9FReW/oqLSfwUFhf+KiopkYwZDE8v/BsYm/3X19KliIACKLTgA+hHFZgAAAABJRU5ErkJggg=='); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <picture>\n          <source\n              srcset=\"/s